SAPO,is,a,Portuguese,Internet,service,provider,whose,main,web,site,acts,as,a,web,portal,featuring,a,directory,of,Portuguese,sites,SAPO,Services,provides,a,large,suite,of,web,services,and,applications,to,developers,worldwide,SemanticLists,is,a,service,that,contains,lists,of,words,organized,into,semantic,categories,Example,categories,include,nationalities,organizations,and,jobs,The,word,lists,are,only,in,Portuguese,at,this,time,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON